                    <span>Fine collection and one we see people refer to very often on discussion lists and web sites. From the simple to the complicated, from the overt to the sublime, you will find some story of value in this book that speaks to you and wants you to speak it. Well worth the price and a book that you will read and tell often.-Storyteller.net Review</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">An Excellent Source of "Wonder Tales"</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
